data.description: Space? This home is a full 4 bedroom home 2 full bath featuring an open and split floorplan.  Laminate flooring, screened in porch, walk in pantry, walk in laundry room with 2 closets in 4th bedroom, storage shed, additional oversized driveway with additional parking, fenced in yard and located in Briarwood adjacent of Holiday Park with NO HOA. Must see to appreciate the space!! Modern Cherry cabinets and rustic  fixtures to set this home off with its on character.  Located right off eagle way bypass for convenient travels to Pennyrile Extension I 24 or Fort Campbell.
